<div class="collection-page" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/CollectionPage">
  <div class="collection-banner">
    <div class="wave-field" aria-hidden="true">
      <span class="wave wave--back"></span>
      <span class="wave wave--mid"></span>
      <span class="wave wave--front"></span>
    </div>
    <div class="section-eyebrow">Functional Mushroom Seltzers · No Alcohol · No Caffeine</div>
    <h1 itemprop="name">{{ collection.title }}</h1>
    {%- if collection.description != blank -%}
      <p itemprop="description">{{ collection.description }}</p>
    {%- else -%}
      <p>Caffeine-free sparkling drinks made with Lion's Mane, Cordyceps and Red Reishi mushrooms, plus magnesium and calcium from ocean minerals. No alcohol, no crash, no artificial sweeteners. Free shipping on every order, no minimum.</p>
    {%- endif -%}
    <div class="coll-banner-chips">
      <span>🍄 100% Fruiting Body</span>
      <span>✅ 0% Alcohol</span>
      <span>⚡ Caffeine-Free</span>
      <span>🧪 Third-Party Lab Tested</span>
      <span>🌿 Vegan &amp; Non-GMO</span>
    </div>
  </div>
  {%- comment -%}
    On the catch-all drink listings (/collections/all and the front page) we hide
    merch — any non-Beverage product. Real drink collections and the dedicated
    merch collection show their own products untouched.
  {%- endcomment -%}
  {%- assign drinks_only = false -%}
  {%- if collection.handle == 'all' or collection.handle == 'frontpage' -%}
    {%- assign drinks_only = true -%}
  {%- endif -%}
  <div class="section-inner">
    <div class="products-grid">
      {% comment %} Sold-out products are skipped so the grid stays one clean row {% endcomment %}
      {% for product in collection.products %}
        {% if product.available and drinks_only == false or product.available and product.type == 'Beverage' %}
          {% render 'product-card', product: product %}
        {% endif %}
      {% endfor %}
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- SEO content block — premium redesign -->
  <div class="coll-seo-section">
    <div class="coll-seo-inner">

      <!-- Header -->
      <div class="coll-seo-header">
        <div class="coll-seo-eyebrow">Why We're Different</div>
        <h2 class="coll-seo-title">Why Happie Fungi Fusion is the best<br>functional mushroom drink</h2>
      </div>

      <!-- Two-col: text + mushroom cards -->
      <div class="coll-seo-grid">
        <div class="coll-seo-text">
          <p>Most mushroom supplements come as capsules made from mycelium grown on grain — which can end up more grain starch than mushroom. Happie Fungi Fusion is different: we use only <strong>fruiting body extracts</strong>, dual-extracted (hot water + ethanol) for the full spectrum of beta-glucans and triterpenes.</p>
          <p>Every 12oz can is <strong>zero alcohol, zero caffeine, 40 calories, 9g sugar and no artificial sweeteners</strong>. Something good to hold at work, before the gym, or when everyone else is holding something. Available in <a href="/products/watermelon-fungi-powered-seltzer">Watermelon</a>, <a href="/products/mango-mimosa-fungi-powered-seltzer">Mango Mimosa</a>, <a href="/products/blue-razzberry-fungi-powered-seltzer">Blue Razzberry</a>, and a <a href="/products/happie-fungi-fusion-mushroom-drink-variety-pack">12-can Variety Pack</a>.</p>
          <!-- Link pills -->
          <div class="coll-seo-links">
            <a href="/pages/the-science" class="coll-seo-link">
              <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M9 3h6l1 4H8L9 3z"/><path d="M8 7v10a1 1 0 0 0 1 1h6a1 1 0 0 0 1-1V7"/><path d="M12 11v3M11 13h2"/></svg>
              The Science of Dual Extraction
            </a>
            <a href="/pages/mushrooms" class="coll-seo-link">
              <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12s4.5 10 10 10 10-4.5 10-10S17.5 2 12 2"/><path d="M8.56 2.75c4.37 6.03 6.02 9.42 8.03 17.72M10.48 21.24c1.94-9.38 5.15-13.84 8.1-18.68"/></svg>
              About the Mushrooms
            </a>
            <a href="/pages/faq" class="coll-seo-link">
              <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><path d="M9.09 9a3 3 0 0 1 5.83 1c0 2-3 3-3 3"/><line x1="12" y1="17" x2="12.01" y2="17"/></svg>
              FAQ
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Mushroom stat cards -->
        <div class="coll-seo-cards">
          <div class="coll-mush-card coll-mush-lion">
            <div class="coll-mush-dose">Lion's Mane</div>
            <div class="coll-mush-name">Hericium erinaceus</div>
            <div class="coll-mush-benefit">At work</div>
            <p class="coll-mush-desc">The one people know by sight — the shaggy white mushroom. Dual-extracted fruiting body, never mycelium on grain.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="coll-mush-card coll-mush-cord">
            <div class="coll-mush-dose">Cordyceps</div>
            <div class="coll-mush-name">Cordyceps militaris</div>
            <div class="coll-mush-benefit">Before the gym</div>
            <p class="coll-mush-desc">An athlete's favourite, and the mushroom behind cordycepin. No caffeine and no stimulants of any kind.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="coll-mush-card coll-mush-rei">
            <div class="coll-mush-dose">Red Reishi</div>
            <div class="coll-mush-name">Ganoderma lucidum</div>
            <div class="coll-mush-benefit">Instead of a beer</div>
            <p class="coll-mush-desc">Centuries of use in Asian wellness traditions, and the richest of the three in triterpenes — which only an alcohol extraction releases.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>

  <style>
  .coll-seo-section {
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, #fff 0%, #F6F8F7 100%);
    padding: 80px 24px;
    border-top: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.06);
  }
  .coll-seo-inner { max-width: 1100px; margin: 0 auto; }

  .coll-seo-header { text-align: center; margin-bottom: 56px; }
  .coll-seo-eyebrow {
    display: inline-block;
    font-size: 11px; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 0.16em; text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--green, #52B788);
    background: rgba(82,183,136,0.1);
    border: 1px solid rgba(82,183,136,0.2);
    padding: 6px 16px; border-radius: 50px;
    margin-bottom: 14px;
  }
  .coll-seo-title {
    font-size: clamp(24px, 3.5vw, 38px);
    font-weight: 900; line-height: 1.15;
    color: var(--green-dark, #2D6A4F);
    margin: 0;
  }

  .coll-seo-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 56px;
    align-items: start;
  }

  .coll-seo-text p {
    font-size: 15px; color: #4A4A4A;
    line-height: 1.85; margin-bottom: 16px;
  }
  .coll-seo-text p:last-of-type { margin-bottom: 28px; }
  .coll-seo-text strong { color: #1A1A1A; }
  .coll-seo-text a {
    color: var(--green, #52B788);
    font-weight: 700; text-decoration: none;
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(82,183,136,0.3);
    transition: border-color 0.2s;
  }
  .coll-seo-text a:hover { border-color: var(--green, #52B788); }

  .coll-seo-links { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 10px; }
  .coll-seo-link {
    display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px;
    background: #fff;
    border: 1.5px solid rgba(82,183,136,0.25);
    border-radius: 50px;
    padding: 10px 18px;
    font-size: 13px; font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--green-dark, #2D6A4F);
    text-decoration: none !important;
    border-bottom: 1.5px solid rgba(82,183,136,0.25) !important;
    width: fit-content;
    transition: all 0.2s;
  }
  .coll-seo-link:hover {
    background: var(--green, #52B788);
    border-color: var(--green, #52B788) !important;
    color: #fff;
    transform: translateX(3px);
  }
  .coll-seo-link svg { flex-shrink: 0; }

  /* Mushroom cards */
  .coll-seo-cards { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 14px; }

  .coll-mush-card {
    border-radius: 20px;
    padding: 24px 26px;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
    border: 1px solid transparent;
    transition: transform 0.2s, box-shadow 0.2s;
  }
  .coll-mush-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-3px);
    box-shadow: 0 12px 32px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
  }
  .coll-mush-lion {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #EBF8F0, #D4EDDE);
    border-color: rgba(82,183,136,0.2);
  }
  .coll-mush-cord {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #FFF8ED, #FDECD0);
    border-color: rgba(245,166,35,0.2);
  }
  .coll-mush-rei {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #F0EEF8, #E2DEEF);
    border-color: rgba(98,96,174,0.2);
  }

  .coll-mush-dose {
    font-size: 28px; font-weight: 900; line-height: 1;
    margin-bottom: 2px;
  }
  .coll-mush-lion .coll-mush-dose { color: var(--green-dark, #2D6A4F); }
  .coll-mush-cord .coll-mush-dose { color: #B45309; }
  .coll-mush-rei .coll-mush-dose { color: #4C3B9A; }

  .coll-mush-dose { font-size: 24px; letter-spacing: -0.01em; }
  .coll-mush-name {
    font-size: 12.5px; font-weight: 600; font-style: italic;
    letter-spacing: 0.01em; margin-bottom: 8px; opacity: 0.85;
  }
  .coll-mush-lion .coll-mush-name { color: var(--green, #52B788); }
  .coll-mush-cord .coll-mush-name { color: #D97706; }
  .coll-mush-rei .coll-mush-name { color: #6260AE; }

  .coll-mush-benefit {
    display: inline-block;
    font-size: 11px; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    padding: 3px 10px; border-radius: 50px;
    margin-bottom: 10px;
  }
  .coll-mush-lion .coll-mush-benefit { background: rgba(82,183,136,0.15); color: var(--green-dark, #2D6A4F); }
  .coll-mush-cord .coll-mush-benefit { background: rgba(245,166,35,0.15); color: #92400E; }
  .coll-mush-rei .coll-mush-benefit { background: rgba(98,96,174,0.15); color: #3730A3; }

  .coll-mush-desc {
    font-size: 13px; color: #555;
    line-height: 1.6; margin: 0;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .coll-seo-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 40px; }
    .coll-seo-section { padding: 60px 20px; }
    .coll-seo-title br { display: none; }
  }
  </style>
</div>

<script type="application/ld+json">
{
  "@context": "https://schema.org",
  "@type": "ItemList",
  "name": "Happie Fungi Fusion Functional Mushroom Seltzers",
  "description": "Caffeine-free sparkling drinks made with Lion's Mane, Cordyceps and Red Reishi mushrooms. Zero alcohol, 40 calories, no artificial sweeteners.",
  "itemListElement": [
    {% for product in collection.products %}{% if drinks_only == false or product.type == 'Beverage' %}
    {
      "@type": "ListItem",
      "position": {{ forloop.index }},
      "name": {{ product.title | json }},
      "url": "https://happiefusion.com/products/{{ product.handle }}",
      "image": "https:{{ product.featured_image | image_url: width: 600 }}",
      "description": {{ product.description | strip_html | truncate: 200 | json }}
    }{% unless forloop.last %},{% endunless %}{% endif %}
    {% endfor %}
  ]
}
</script>

{% schema %}
{
  "name": "Main Collection",
  "settings": []
}
{% endschema %}
